worthwhile /ˌwɜːθˈwaɪl/

1. ADJ If something is worthwhile , it is enjoyable or useful, and worth the time, money, or effort that is spent on it. 值得的 

例： The president's trip to Washington this week seems to have been worthwhile. 该总统本周的华盛顿之行似乎是值得的。

